  <div class="catering-img"><img src="/images/van.jpg" alt="Los Cabos catering" loading="lazy" /></div>
  <div class="catering-text">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Events &amp; Catering</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">WE COME<br>TO YOU.</h2>
    <p class="catering-sub">Real Tex-Mex. Your location. We handle everything from setup to the last tortilla.</p>
