      <li>Weddings, corporate events &amp; private parties</li>
      <li>Custom menus built around your event</li>
      <li>Groups of 20 to 500+</li>
      <li>Full setup and breakdown included</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="tel:+15126076232" class="btn-primary">Call to Book — (512) 607-6232</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="reviews-section">
  <div class="reviews-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Google Reviews</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:white;">WHAT OUR REGULARS<br>ARE SAYING</h2>
