  </div>
  <div class="reviews-grid">
    <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">"Best fajitas in Austin County. The sizzling platter comes out perfect every time."</p><div class="review-name">— Maria G.</div></div>
    <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">"The margaritas are incredible and the queso is free during lunch. Service is always fast and friendly."</p><div class="review-name">— James T.</div></div>
    <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">"Catered our company party and blew everyone away. Professional, on time, outstanding food."</p><div class="review-name">— Sandra R.</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="find-section" id="find-us">
  <div class="find-content">
    <div><div class="section-eyebrow">Come In</div><h2 class="section-heading">FIND US</h2></div>
    <div class="find-row"><span class="find-label">Address</span><span class="find-value">6027 FM 3538 Rd<br>Sealy, TX 77474</span></div>
    <div class="find-row"><span class="find-label">Phone</span><span class="find-value"><a href="tel:+15126076232">(512) 607-6232</a></span></div>
    <div class="find-row"><span class="find-label">Hours</span><span class="find-value">Sun-Wed: 11AM - 9PM<br>Thu-Sat: 11AM - 10PM</span></div>
